Alternating Flux (NeoForge port)

Original mod "Alternating Flux" created by AntiBlueQuirk (Minecraft 1.12.2).
This is an updated port to Minecraft 1.21.1 / NeoForge by Arctonix.

This port is shared publicly with the explicit permission of the original
author, AntiBlueQuirk. The concept, design, and original artwork are theirs.

